            <p class="text-text-muted text-xs">5 years supporting C-suite through pre-IPO</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-secondary mt-1">&#8226;</span>
